25/02/2008
PODGORICA, Montenegro -- President Filip Vujanovic says Montenegro will be "careful and level-headed regarding Kosovo".
During a speech in the port city of Bar on Friday (February 22nd), where he launched his campaign for the April 6th presidential elections, he added that Montenegro should maintain good relations with Serbia.
Vujanovic leaves on Monday for a two-day official visit to Brussels, where he is to meet with EU and NATO officials.
(Focus - 25/02/08;
Tanjug, B92- 24/02/08;
RTCG - 22/02/08)
